Purpose: Manage quizzes, questions, and options

Actions:
- createQuiz({ owner, title }) -> { quiz } | { error }
- deleteQuiz({ quiz }) -> { quiz } | { error }
- updateQuizTitle({ quiz, title }) -> { quiz } | { error }
- addQuestion({ quiz, text }) -> { question } | { error }
- deleteQuestion({ question }) -> { question } | { error }
- updateQuestion({ question, text }) -> { question } | { error }
- addOption({ question, label }) -> { option } | { error }
- deleteOption({ option }) -> { option } | { error }
- updateOption({ option, label }) -> { option } | { error }

Queries:
- _getQuizzesByOwner({ owner }) -> [{ quiz, title }]
- _getQuiz({ quiz }) -> [{ quiz, owner, title }]
- _getQuestions({ quiz }) -> [{ question, text }]
- _getOptions({ question }) -> [{ option, label }]
- _getQuestion({ question }) -> [{ question, text, quiz }]

State (MongoDB):
- quizzes: { quiz, owner, title }
- questions: { question, quiz, text }
- options: { option, question, label }

